      "text": "We have to teach people and educate the people that this, what happened, was a crime, not only against the Jew, or Poles, or gypsies, or anybody else they murder, 11 million people-- it's a crime committed by the whole world because the world didn't stand up to stomp it out and stop Hitler to doing what he did.",
