      "text": "It's a difficult task because survivor didn't open right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were only few individual cases who start to talk about this since the liberation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, after the interesting movie of and so many books what came on the market, what telling the truth, now the people start to understand the importance of this particular education of this horrible period of Hitler, and Stalin in-- in the-- in the-- in Europe.",
